<h2>OFFICE OF SUSTAINABILITY ANNOUNCES CATERPILLAR SUSTAINABILITY SCHOLARSHIPS, APPLICATION DEADLINE OCTOBER 31, 2011</h2>
<p><em>October 26, 2011</em></p>
<p>The Office of Sustainability is pleased to announce up to six scholarship awards of $1000-$1500 each, applied toward tuition. The Caterpillar Sustainability Scholarship awards undergraduate students who:</p>
<ul>
<li>Demonstrate active involvement in sustainability initiatives in their communities;</li>
<li>Think creatively about approaching these issues on campus;</li>
<li>Bring diversity to their field of study; and</li>
<li>Achieve academically.</li>
</ul>
<p>For more information visit the <a href="http://www.uic.edu/sustainability/" target="_blank">Office of Sustainability</a> scholarship <a href="http://www.uic.edu/sustainability/academics/catscholarship.html" target="_blank">webpage</a></td>
